name: Burger Set for Two
description: A burger meal for two bought at a chain fast food restaurant popular in many cities. The taste and size of the burgers is perfect. It's just that the set only includes 1 cup of Dr. Cinnamon, which may lead to the ice melting into the drink as the two diners each try to let the other enjoy it.
usage: Edible product used to restore Sanity. Will be consumed upon receipt. Ready to eat.
